    "Ethical and Legal Concerns: Using language models for diagnostic medicine raises ethical and legal concerns.",
    "Patient privacy, data security, liability, and accountability are important considerations when deploying these models in clinical settings.",
    "Ensuring proper consent, protecting patient information, and mitigating potential biases in the models are critical aspects that need to be addressed. 4.",
